"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       <b>",
"        EDD by LMP",
"       </b>",
"       is calculated by adding 280 days (40 weeks) to the first day of the last menstrual period.",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       <b>",
"        Gestational Age by US",
"       </b>",
"       is measured by ultrasound (US) on the",
"       <b>",
"        Ultrasound Date",
"       </b>",
"       .",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       <b>",
"        EDD by US",
"       </b>",
"       is the estimated date of delivery based on the",
"       <b>",
"        Gestational Age by US",
"       </b>",
"       and the",
"       <b>",
"        Ultrasound Date",
"       </b>",
"       .",
"      </li>",
"     </ul>",
"    </div>",
"    <br/>",
"    &nbsp;",
"    <br/>",
